{
  "stem": "1062.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, it wasn't-- no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It wasn't a web.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I just want to bring out how people used to make their own clothes.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In other words, from the flags they made not a web.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was called-- like, weaving. weaving.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They would set up in the house like, weaving.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was a whole-- it took up, like, the whole living room there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They would set it up, and then they would take old rags, whatever they had left over, and they would weave it into this thing with the flags, you know?",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You make carpets out of it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If you didn't want to make carpets, then they would weave this material, and they would make clothes out of it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's flax seed clothes, it's like a very rough-- it looks like denim.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Maybe my village was 50 years ahead of the times because they made denim there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But it was-- it was-- this-- they used to make their own clothes.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then from, from the sheep, they would make shoes where they would put a lot of rags in with the skin, make shoes.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And not necessarily the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The Jewish people were more, were more-- you know, they, they would dress a little-- not different, they didn't.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But I'm just talking the local people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the life was very good.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I mean, compared to what was coming, it was good.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Because what's happening now is this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[CLEARS THROAT] I don't want to get into politics, but we all know, you know, in Russia, there was the Soviet Union, and they had their interest in Nazi Germany and [?",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Nottingham. ?] And the British and the French, you know, they would appease us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You know the whole story.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But what happens is in 1939, Germany invades Poland.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "The Russian Army-- the Russians give an ultimatum for Romania to surrender the Eastern provinces of Bessarabia and Bukovina.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "My father, he was in the Romanian Army.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "He was at one time in the Romanian Army.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "He was an artillery man.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "He was called in to-- he was called in because the Russians gave an ultimatum to surrender those provinces.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I remember seeing my father off from the village, and he went into the army.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But of course, no war broke out, because when the ultimatum expired, the Russians, they came.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They say they came in planes and the Romanian Army surrendered.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And they withdrew from Bessarabia and Bukovina, and they gave it over to the Russians.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "The Romanian government blamed the Jews.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "They claimed that the Jews were a fifth column in the country, and they were supposedly allied with the Communists to take over those provinces.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "So anti-Semitism started to raise its ugly head very badly in Romania.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "In the meantime, France fell.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Romania didn't have no allies, so she made an alliance with Germany.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Hungary was an ally of Germany all the time because it was part of the Austro-Hungarian empire once.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "So the Hungarians put claim to the province of Transylvania, of Transylvania.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And those two people, the Romanians and the Hungarians, they're blood enemies, and they were ready to go to war.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "So they met in Vienna, which is called the Vienna Diktat.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Ribbentrop was there and Ciano from Italy, and they took Transylvania and they divide it in half.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "The northern part of Transylvania was ceded to Hungary.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And this was in August, 1940, around there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Maybe in July, August 1940.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Now, at this point, the Hungarian Army came in and took over the northern part of Transylvania, where my village was located.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "We, the Jewish people, were a little bit happy because in Romania, things were getting hot.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "The iron guard in the, in the government were blaming the Jews for the province of-- for losing the province of Bessarabia.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "So we thought that we're going to be rescued by the Hungarians.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the Hungarians came in in 1940, and we were part of Hungary.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Of course, I didn't speak no Hungarian then, but they sent-- they send a teacher to the-- a Hungarian teacher to my school, and you know, I, I started to learn the language.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Romanian population in Comlausa, my village, were also oppressed because the Hungarian used to take them for forced labor.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they hated the Romanians.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then the war broke out with Russia in-- with the Soviet Union between Germany and, and the Soviet Union.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was in 1941, in June.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The end of 1941, Hungary declared war on the Soviet Union.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PHONE RINGING] And they went ahead, and they took all the Jewish men, and they, and they were conscripted into the army.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PHONE RINGING] And-- [PHONE RINGING] --they were conscripted into the army.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Not into the army, into a work battalion.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
